The corresponding XML element is /TED_EXPORT/FORM_SECTION/F13_2014/COMPLEMENTARY_INFO/ADDRESS_REVIEW_INFO/ADDRESS. The expected ontology instances are epo: epo:AgentInRole (from CL1) / org:Organization (from CL2) /  locn:Address / rdf:langString .
query.query:
PREFIX cv: <http://data.europa.eu/m8g/>
PREFIX epo: <http://data.europa.eu/a4g/ontology#>
PREFIX locn: <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

ASK WHERE { 
		?this rdf:type epo:ReviewProcedureInformationProvider .
		?this epo:playedBy / cv:registeredAddress / locn:thoroughfare ?value . }
query.title: VI.4.4.2 - Postal address
